<h2>Your Role Has Been Updated</h2>

<p>Hello {{firstName}},</p>

<p>This is to notify you that your platform administrator role has been changed.</p>

<div class="info-box">
  <p><strong>Role Change Details:</strong></p>
  <p>Previous Role: <strong>{{oldRole}}</strong><br>
  New Role: <strong>{{newRole}}</strong><br>
  Changed By: {{changedBy}}<br>
  Date: {{changeDate}}</p>
</div>

{{#if isPromotion}}
<p>Congratulations on your expanded responsibilities! Your new role grants you additional privileges and access to more platform features.</p>
{{else}}
<p>Your role has been updated. Please review your current permissions in the platform settings.</p>
{{/if}}

<a href="{{platformUrl}}/settings" class="button">View Your Permissions</a>

<div class="divider"></div>

<p><strong>What's changed:</strong></p>
{{{roleDescription}}}

<p>If you have any questions about your new role or permissions, please contact the platform administrator who made this change.</p>

<p>Best regards,<br>
<strong>OMS Platform Team</strong></p>
